	quests: [
		{
			description: [
				"Fishing. It truly is something special, isn't it? Well, here you'll find there's much to do and much to find."
				"But all fishermen need one item. What is it? Why, a fishing rod of course! So, why don't you craft one, and we can get this aquatic show on the road?"
			]
